data.text:
Full Name: Mohit Bagri

Birthplace: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India

Birthdate: April 20th 2002 Occupation: Child Actor

Years: 2011-Active

Role: Rocky Malhotra

Mohit Bagri (born on May 28 2000) is a child actor who first appears in Disney Channel India's new show named Oye Jassie.He played the role Rishi who later became Rocky Malhotra in Disney Channel India's Oye Jassie.

He also appears in a Crax add.He even acted in a Tata sky sing along with karaoke for kids.
